Class SimpleRatingBar.AnimationBuilder

  • java.lang.Object

  • Enclosing class:
    SimpleRatingBar

    public class SimpleRatingBar.AnimationBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class to build rating animation. Provides good defaults: - Target rating: numberOfStars - Animation: Bounce - Duration: 2s
